text: “brrda mu na fik chay læa brrda mu na fik hying nan bang swn khxng phwk khea tang ma cak xik bang swn sung phwk khea ca chı hı ptibati nı sing thi mi chxb læa hampram nı sing thi chxb læa kamux khxng phwk khea wi doythi phwk khea lum xallxh læw phraxngkh k thrng lum phwk khea bang thæcring brrda mu na fik nan phwk khea khux phu lameid”
